{"tid":1562690,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"【願榮光歸香港】要改善的三個位","createTime":"2019-09-12T06:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T16:30:00.000Z","uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e3f1cc1d2c502a48b0a6cd01d01a046bc81fef","tid":1562690,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:15:22.000Z","msg":"以下是我一位專業填詞人的朋友的意見：<br />\n<br />\n1. 其實歌詞拒「默沉」係大敗筆位黎 🤔,<br />\n啲詞語唔係個個可以咁倒轉寫 🤔<br />\n<br />\n改詞建議：?<br />\n<br />\n2. 來全力「抗對」又係 😩<br />\n<br />\n改詞建議：捍自由 來齊集這裡 來<span style=\"color: red;\">除掉怨懟</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 同埋結尾個香港音高從上而下係唔靚，尤其個港字如果跟足音唱聽落會似個降字，在意頭上都唔太好 🙃<br />\n<br />\n改詞建議：關鍵位，好棘手。"},{"pid":"d62b6e699fac7eef2a29de6a59232a772244999b","tid":1562690,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:16:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0886d66cdec1c15ab77d8b230fc3dbfde3e42b84","tid":1562690,"uid":201902,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"推啊啊啊"},{"pid":"1b92faeefc52aafba7d16cdd10e8df9dd4029d31","tid":1562690,"uid":52949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:25:23.000Z","msg":"臨尾個香港  真係難唱"},{"pid":"fd9f0f4db3db70a74d24f76bee21ba78642a6c89","tid":1562690,"